            "title": "Adorno, o fascismo e o mal",
            "abstract": [
                "One of the thinkers of the 20th century who most devoted himself to the critical study of fascism was the German philosopher and sociologist Theodor Adorno. His work detailed the emotional vulnerability of ordinary citizens to prejudices, appeals to group membership and destructive rage directed against victims of fascist persecution. In carrying out his critical analysis, Adorno mainly employed concepts from Freudian psychoanalysis and dialectical materialism. This book presents Adorno's critical study of fascism, but also seeks to demonstrate that the destructiveness and cruelty of fascism go beyond the analysis proposed by Adorno, and therefore require the use of the concept of metaphysical evil for its broader understanding. With this objective, the first part of the work exposes the central theoretical elements used by Adorno to understand and criticize fascism. In the second part, the most important philosophical concepts are exposed to understand the metaphysical concept of evil and also its implications related to the field of education",
                "Um dos pensadores do s\u00e9culo XX que mais se dedicou ao estudo cr\u00edtico do fascismo foi o fil\u00f3sofo e soci\u00f3logo alem\u00e3o Theodor Adorno. Seu trabalho detalhou a vulnerabilidade emocional do cidad\u00e3o comum a preconceitos, apelos de ades\u00e3o grupal e de f\u00faria destrutiva dirigidos contra as v\u00edtimas da persegui\u00e7\u00e3o fascista. Na realiza\u00e7\u00e3o de sua an\u00e1lise cr\u00edtica, Adorno empregou principalmente conceitos da psican\u00e1lise freudiana e do materialismo dial\u00e9tico. Este livro apresenta o estudo cr\u00edtico de Adorno sobre o fascismo, mas tamb\u00e9m procura demonstrar que a destrutividade e crueldade do fascismo extrapolam a an\u00e1lise proposta por Adorno, e por isso requerem o emprego do conceito de mal metaf\u00edsico para sua compreens\u00e3o mais ampla. Com esse objetivo, a primeira parte do trabalho exp\u00f5e os elementos te\u00f3ricos centrais utilizados por Adorno para entender e criticar o fascismo. Na segunda parte, s\u00e3o expostos os conceitos filos\u00f3ficos mais importantes para se compreender o conceito metaf\u00edsico de mal e tamb\u00e9m suas implica\u00e7\u00f5es relacionadas com o campo da educa\u00e7\u00e3o"
            ],
